                                                                                                               PC snub
                            
	Bangalore, March 20: The Union home minister visited Karnataka today but did not meet the chief minister. The act, being seen as a snub to B.S. Yeddyurappa, came after the home ministrys claim that the BJP chief minister had repeatedly stalled P. Chidambarams visit.                                                                                                                                                                                                     
